  2.21: 21.12.1998
    - better error checking
  2.2: 14.12.1998
    - new function IsOpen
    - lots of SetLastError(0) calls added
  2.12: 28.10.1998
    - CreateEx enhanced
  2.11: 14.10.1998
    - error reporting in Block*Unsafe enhanced
  2.1: 13.10.1998
    - FilePos works in buffered mode
    - faster FilePos in unbuffered mode
